Zambia II Compact - Access to Financial Service Project - Project Preparation Facility (PPF) Activity: The Zambia Project Preparation Facility for EILP (ZAMPPF Activity) aims to increase the number of EILP infrastructure projects that support agriculture value chains to reach financial close by providing:
1. Technical assistance to project developers (e.g., GRZ and private developers) to develop bankable EILP infrastructure projects;
2. Technical assistance and capacity building for public and private project developers.
